  "description": "<p><strong>7月12日下午消息，昨日有网友爆料称自己购买的乐视超级电视突然爆炸，引发业界关注。今日乐视对此事回应称，故障的超级电视属于电源板上单个元器件失效，而非“爆炸”。</strong>目前乐视已为用户更换新机，出故障的超级电视将会公开展示。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e8ec7f1/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244468.htm&amp;t=%E4%B9%90%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%B3%BB%E5%85%83%E5%99%A8%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244468.htm&amp;t=%E4%B9%90%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%B3%BB%E5%85%83%E5%99%A8%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244468.htm&amp;t=%E4%B9%90%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%B3%BB%E5%85%83%E5%99%A8%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244468.htm&amp;t=%E4%B9%90%E8%A7%86%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%94%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%B3%BB%E5%85%83%E5%99%A8%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%